entries.arrived_at_delivery: My pilot will be here shortly to pick up the spices.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Spices have been transfered. Nice working with you.
entries.found_loc_d: Pilot, I'm transmitting the location at which you'll meet my employee. As soon as you reach them, transfer the spice.
entries.hello_d: I am assuming we are both working for Mr. Scutu? Good, dock with me when you are ready.
entries.quest_dock2_d: To dock with the ship, target their ship and press 'U'.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Maghr Scutu's pilot has arrived. Go ahead with docking procedures.
entries.split_quest_alert: Maghr Scutu: <Good job. Come on back to the station, Tarand will settle your account.>
entries.title: Smuggling: The Delivery
entries.title_d: You are to dock with Maghr Scutu's pilot.
